{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "2b237a0d-d8eb-43be-bd34-3361a77ab09f", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2b237a0d-d8eb-43be-bd34-3361a77ab09f@1.pkg/1772597688201/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597688990", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2b237a0d-d8eb-43be-bd34-3361a77ab09f@1.pkg/1772597688201/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597688990"}, "identifier": "2b237a0d-d8eb-43be-bd34-3361a77ab09f", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查理解真正的友谊的价值。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：&ldquo;友谊仅建立在物质帮助基础之上&rdquo;说法过于绝对，真正的友谊往往是超脱物质关系的。因此A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：&ldquo;只有需要付出的友谊才是平等的&rdquo;说法错误，平等的友谊不一定意味着付出，而是意味着相互帮助，相辅相成，因此B错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：&ldquo;真正的友谊需要避免所有的竞争&rdquo;说法过于绝对，友谊也需要一定的良性竞争，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：题目的主旨就是要表达相互帮助才能结成真正的友谊，友谊需要用行动表达关怀与支持，D选项符合题意。因此D正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选D</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）为了帮助因先天性疾病而无法行走的小亮同学，全班同学组成互助小分队，男生负责背他上下楼，女生负责背书包。在同学们的帮助下，小亮与同学们一起度过了快乐的中学时光。这让我们体会到（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）为了帮助因先天性疾病而无法行走的小亮同学，全班同学组成互助小分队，男生负责背他上下楼，女生负责背书包。在同学们的帮助下，小亮与同学们一起度过了快乐的中学时光。这让我们体会到（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2b237a0d-d8eb-43be-bd34-3361a77ab09f@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977936308", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>友谊仅建立在物质帮助基础之上 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>只有需要付出的友谊才是平等的</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>真正的友谊需要避免所有的竞争 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>友谊需要用行动表达关怀与支持</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）为了帮助因先天性疾病而无法行走的小亮同学，全班同学组成互助小分队，男生负责背他上下楼，女生负责背书包。在同学们的帮助下，小亮与同学们一起度过了快乐的中学时光。这让我们体会到（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "e